IURÉTICOS → PRIMERA LÍNEA","guid":"H7tYPJ5NSOa1iEvNotjJHg","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Furosemida IV → base del tratamiento congestión","guid":"bGHV3EatTwuDotntFJh8Xg","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"DOSIS INICIAL","guid":"3E03V5uVRjyfAZeUJl0U7Q","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Naive: 20-40 mg IV bolo","guid":"nKAZbDP-TsuGXohxDlC_jA","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Uso crónico: dosis IV = 1-2.5x dosis oral diaria","guid":"I8NjV-xATzy8l4P9WwttGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"160","parent":"156","text":"DOSE trial → dosis alta vs baja: similar eficacia, ↑ Cr transitoria","guid":"ygqib_ukQf6ib-Un5k7sYA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"156","text":"Objetivo: diuresis >100-150 mL/h en primeras 6h","guid":"CuYX1ZYUQ8yrQpZ66BEQzA","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"156","text":"Si respuesta insuficiente","guid":"yUaGXmA7TYi3Udclkz2XEQ","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"Duplicar dosis (max bolo 200 mg)","guid":"54bV-qjAQlOuU-WwGbhJUA","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"Infusión continua: 5-40 mg/h","guid":"lwG-eyhGRhuccFACLXWhzw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"Asociar tiazida (metolazona 2.5-5 mg VO) → bloqueo secuencial nefrona","guid":"zS1UIjrsSXagXMYGv5nxFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"156","text":"MONITORIZAR: K+, Na+, Cr, peso diario","guid":"8hyWrgB5RX-q-9WRsXrQWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"155","text":"GERIÁTRICO → mayor sensibilidad","guid":"EtDlcSLaQzqH0khtZ6YbRg","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"Riesgo hipovolemia, hiponatremia, hipokalemia","guid":"rJgxJDQ9R4i7IhOk8RrqKA","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"IRA prerrenal → ajustar según diuresis/Cr","guid":"LOO9dJKeTZOt7CIKqwoBLw","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"Ototoxicidad con dosis altas","guid":"RZ1T12MORMuihmgZ4PGa3A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"154","text":"VASODILATADORES (perfil caliente-húmedo, PAS >110)","guid":"YVOfOEiwQ4uMhjatJxcpPQ","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"Nitroglicerina IV → 10-200 μg/min","guid":"ICZ_z1XxTLqTWOI1iE9udw","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"↓ Precarga y postcarga","guid":"W1KOWpQ6Rj2KDCZQwQkmDw","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"Útil en EPA hipertensivo","guid":"3AIKtEsYTCu7qvfanx_-fQ","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"PRECAUCIÓN: estenosis aórtica severa","guid":"oIkYpLJZSVaVVQynueNEDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"Nitroprusiato → reservar HTA severa/IM aguda","guid":"lIsTvgNSRWOAyTjsxS1meQ","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Toxicidad cianuro → no >48h, no en ERC","guid":"r5chGsFCRuuDUEPaarWG1w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"154","text":"OXIGENOTERAPIA Y SOPORTE VENTILATORIO","guid":"XWXmdt_SQEGz3ENy-P25jA","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"O2 solo si SatO2 <90%","guid":"MXvmQ7hwT4KThn9R46M2Qw","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"Hiperoxia → vasoconstricción, ↑ RVS → evitar","guid":"ndjxSqvuSNan89F2M9yLOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"VMNI → EPA o distrés con hipoxemia refractaria","guid":"lwCZi5LzRT2xkSD1tgIeIg","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"CPAP 5-10 cmH2O o BiPAP (IPAP 10-15, EPAP 5-10)","guid":"r5s-quC6Ri-Wu9eynIgNaA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"↓ Intubación, ↓ disnea","guid":"0FwBxH3cTsOpj30F66SP_A","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"GERIÁTRICO: intolerancia frecuente, riesgo delirium por máscara","guid":"Yno6UE-MTHOWHP_JTiU9Gg","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"178","text":"CNAF → alternativa emergente en IC (menos evidencia)","guid":"wuXDuu48S8CeTCFUTNfi6A","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"178","text":"IOT → falla VMNI, deterioro conciencia, shock","guid":"P8qMtloVReeWavci1YDJ8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"154","text":"INOTRÓPICOS (perfil frío-húmedo/seco)","guid":"vie29UDTTaOJpxq0dg9E_Q","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"Dobutamina 2-20 μg/kg/min","guid":"OnW7B1SWRO6zmOcEZ9g5ZQ","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"↑ IC, ↑ FC → riesgo arritmias","guid":"bsDrONi6SyCROTgu_X1p2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"Milrinona 0.375-0.75 μg/kg/min","guid":"dsHzqNuQQ868qAN5gysJBg","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"Inhibidor PDE3 → inodilatador","guid":"q1x3AUDFQJOmFkJLmglYCA","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"Ajustar en ERC","guid":"Mk8N5XcKRt6-AqnmAiRC8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"187","text":"Levosimendán 0.05-0.2 μg/kg/min","guid":"LfYkkGC4TtaETzIWsZkLXg","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"Sensibilizador calcio → no ↑ consumo O2","guid":"N1C63KloQFa4_rzbeglfYA","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"T1/2 larga → efecto persiste días","guid":"CXHA2YW8Sdyc9rv4Sat59A","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"LIDO/SURVIVE trials → sin beneficio mortalidad claro","guid":"Y7IMV7fMT5CjGxiMh-2vpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"187","text":"NORADRENALINA → si shock + vasodilatación","guid":"6fyiJg10RIuEWR__ob9wow","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Preferir sobre dopamina (SOAP II trial)","guid":"XatNIz3lR32CKRrfDyYQhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"199","parent":"187","text":"GERIÁTRICO → inotrópicos ↑ arritmias en AM","guid":"M66S6OVLSrK-Ck7lnBJG7w","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"Menor dosis, titular lento","guid":"B4p3EGdITv-z-z1thjtZgg","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"199","text":"Evaluar proporcionalidad","guid":"RUWY0FoqTBmffNCNn8Mf9Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"154","text":"TRATAMIENTO PRECIPITANTE","guid":"Wf0OeU8tTWGCgJDXAzg84w","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"FA rápida → control FC (digoxina, amiodarona, BB si estable)","guid":"fL0fXKaUSHKZpYnEufrGSg","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"RACE II → FC <110 en reposo aceptable en AM","guid":"hPX_PClcQ9ewszbfCQoNgA","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"SCA → según protocolo (ver mapa SCA)","guid":"KLuu4thzR1OjfAiyEq-WDw","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"Infección → ATB precoz","guid":"a8HNp_66Q1uAyg0t9G1ewA","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"Anemia → transfusión si Hb <7 o sintomática","guid":"w8peQ8rOS3CTAVcbfwEuDQ","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"Corrección electrolitos","guid":"-O7f6T0aSxelGYM_iy47hg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"0","text":"TERAPIA CRÓNICA EN URGENCIAS (NO suspender)","guid":"aXSEgSNzT7-HH4tN_Q873g","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"IC-FEr → TERAPIA CUÁDRUPLE (ESC 2021/AHA 2022)","guid":"ljASlLZZQK-Xrwj_KtAGlQ","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"IECA/ARA2 o ARNI (sacubitril/valsartán)","guid":"YFcAztW7ThanPYewCVIU2g","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"PARADIGM-HF → ARNI superior a enalapril","guid":"NoJzalbMSuGyHXx4rGO9zA","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"PRECAUCIÓN: hipotensión, hiperK, IRA","guid":"DobYiCsfSAimL0kYeNWlqA","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"GERIÁTRICO: iniciar dosis baja, titular lento","guid":"p_G9v33jT36xDqf070AgFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"210","text":"Betabloqueador (bisoprolol, carvedilol, metoprolol succinato)","guid":"oPzAG4yjSXyj70ziDJaPlg","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"NO iniciar en descompensación aguda","guid":"7B6wBRVnQN-wlxVIVYMaww","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"NO suspender si uso crónico (excepto shock/bradicardia severa)","guid":"8BpNy42uT6CZl1MumWoYIA","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"215","text":"Si suspendido → reintroducir antes del alta","guid":"VXJKA351SKSbDOh54UNT_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"210","text":"ARM (espironolactona/eplerenona)","guid":"FigLzJnmTpiNwMydw5GtiQ","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"RALES trial → ↓ mortalidad 30%","guid":"_na0UScjTyCPCYU46Tg3RQ","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"GERIÁTRICO: monitorizar K+ y Cr (hiperK frecuente en AM + ERC)","guid":"-7q7RUpcS9Gqle1lAb0AKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"210","text":"iSGLT2 (dapagliflozina/empagliflozina)","guid":"7J3Jyg1CQ6CY5mMDuNBxhg","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"DAPA-HF + EMPEROR-Reduced → beneficio clase I","guid":"3OF65KI_SnW8fhm7jC38aQ","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"EMPULSE trial → iniciar durante hospitalización es seguro","guid":"M6S1GVmwT5OO6rlXixvRQw","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"DELIVER + EMPEROR-Preserved → beneficio también en IC-FEp","guid":"rMyF6w_5TFmSiwBfruQJyQ","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"GERIÁTRICO: riesgo ITU, hipotensión, deshidratación","guid":"fxkgOO5MQzWIpVEgHfTvHg","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"Ajuste: no iniciar si VFGe <20","guid":"OxaMTwWxR-6C8lKpjVEigQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"Vigilar depleción volumen en AM con diuréticos","guid":"Pb7-2qmmSeaotuDhOEmjpw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"209","text":"IC-FEp → tratamiento limitado","guid":"hP8c7qaZTZKG1U0FqNF6Fw","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"Diuréticos para congestión","guid":"POoDm44xTiW2gJPnrjnQyA","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"iSGLT2 → único con evidencia clase I (DELIVER/EMPEROR-Preserved)","guid":"CM0SAOSMR2CEZoI1nvhg5A","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"Control comorbilidades (HTA, FA, obesidad, diabetes)","guid":"PXNsY8uuTpyymwMoUe8uew","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"0","text":"SITUACIONES ESPECIALES GERIÁTRICAS","guid":"391BKAHmR2yxASCVksHUUQ","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"IC + FA","guid":"RZ5-jRs5R4m1Qnw4GLZ0kw","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"Coexistencia frecuente (>50% en AM con IC)","guid":"I2mobrvvR2iafhu323og8w","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"Control FC > control ritmo en la mayoría AM","guid":"kEM-RecsS525kZ_-ACbfNQ","children":[]},{"id":"237","par