"guid":"kyXLndshS_Gl-97_R_Dz3Q","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"250","text":"AFFIRM-AHF → carboximaltosa férrica IV ↓ rehospitalización","guid":"ooifbQ_9QOSTeU8WMyHiFw","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"250","text":"Criterio: ferritina <100 o ferritina 100-299 + IST <20%","guid":"FquHtwH0S32uxoMpM8Nzpg","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"250","text":"GERIÁTRICO: hierro IV preferido sobre oral (↑ absorción, ↓ GI)","guid":"P4L8ZoMvQoanYzJabANe8w","children":[]}]},{"id":"256","parent":"233","text":"PACIENTE FRÁGIL","guid":"sop7WI7vS6qJRT9adYfw5w","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"CFS ≥6 → evaluar objetivos de cuidado","guid":"UAisntUHRM2d_Oco1JiXUg","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"256","text":"Polifarmacia: deprescripción proactiva","guid":"LpOWWCq0QeC-hxbHtQe82w","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"256","text":"STOPP/START integrar → suspender fármacos sin beneficio","guid":"S3xWBT2wQ2qabDxXbbQofA","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"256","text":"Rehabilitación precoz: movilización temprana","guid":"SSrD7Q1eT4mHP5jfyPetIw","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"256","text":"Nutrición: screening MNA, suplementar proteínas","guid":"4tgetrgKS2KEF_ud1lWbuA","children":[]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"233","text":"PACIENTE PALIATIVO","guid":"mkF0fRIpSUCi5xGTYJnfeg","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"IC terminal (NYHA IV refractaria, múltiples hospitalizaciones)","guid":"wCqOI33XSJayJyThzJyc2w","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"262","text":"Discutir VIA (voluntades anticipadas)","guid":"KcZjeXTfSfi4MMmooSLpJA","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"262","text":"Mantener diuréticos para control síntomas","guid":"xwEHlTGhRYGRiAGcHyzUXA","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"262","text":"Opioides: morfina baja dosis → disnea refractaria","guid":"gcgf-sRtTlCXusd7H3FhSA","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"262","text":"Considerar desactivación DAI si implantado","guid":"mcq6FOdlThSaSukED0O1WA","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"262","text":"