xt":"LR+ 5-10 o LR- 0.1-0.2 -> cambio MODERADO (IY, reflujo HY, NT-proBNP alto)","guid":"EJGmyQvJQhysr9x8o18H-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"331","parent":"306","text":"GERIATRIA","guid":"pdydVWA-Qq2uoezfHQm5FQ","children":[{"id":"332","parent":"331","text":"Usar NT-proBNP con cortes ajustados por edad (PRIDE trial)","guid":"A9jbiVTNT1O2Fpv39IQegA","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"331","text":"S3 es el hallazgo individual mas potente","guid":"k7YlLTWzQ4-Ao-ymScoR_A","children":[]},{"id":"334","parent":"331","text":"POCUS pulmonar (lineas B) cada vez mas validado en urgencias","guid":"Jpz7Bj11TZG0C0OENO1b1A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"335","parent":"0","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"NnEl_DtCSkexUngBK1_daw","children":[{"id":"336","parent":"335","text":"ESC 2021 Guidelines Acute/Chronic Heart Failure (McDonagh et al, Eur Heart J 2021)","guid":"QZQuJ_GgSL207TZk_H4fHA","children":[]},{"id":"337","parent":"335","text":"AHA/ACC/HFSA 2022 Heart Failure Guidelines (Heidenreich et al, Circulation 2022)","guid":"9DA6jQvQQ8yFRfGkWM2vSQ","children":[]},{"id":"338","parent":"335","text":"PARADIGM-HF → sacubitril/valsartán (McMurray et al, NEJM 2014)","guid":"TpVNcrxXS6W1-_dzepIATw","children":[]},{"id":"339","parent":"335","text":"DAPA-HF → dapagliflozina IC-FEr (McMurray et al, NEJM 2019)","guid":"a2Mk2sxITjaVgNLc3RrVpg","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"335","text":"EMPEROR-Reduced → empagliflozina IC-FEr (Packer et al, NEJM 2020)","guid":"jyBCSVv9S6C9Kxv9_4epbQ","children":[]},{"id":"341","parent":"335","text":"DELIVER → dapagliflozina IC-FEp (Solomon et al, NEJM 2022)","guid":"FGvyR_yeTBmvswc1TjVeEg","children":[]},{"id":"342","parent":"335","text":"EMPULSE → iSGLT2 en hospitalización (Voors et al, Nat Med 2022)","guid":"4HPEO8LDSmi6mIrDuxyiZw","children":[]},{"id":"343","parent":"335","text":"AFFIRM-AHF → hierro IV en IC (Ponikowski et al, Lancet 2020)","guid":"enkOcVu4RAmrYDAqjMDvog","children":[]},{"id":"344","parent":"335","text":"DOSE trial → furosemida dosis (Felker et